  <official_title>SERENITY: Evaluating the Effectiveness of Atypical Antipsychotics in the Community - a Prospective, Multicentre, Observational Study to Evaluate the Impact on Quality of Life of GP-Bases Management of Antipsychotic Treatment in Belgium.</official_title>
